high_descs: Turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of the left sink.
Go to the right sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn left to face the bottom cabinets.
Open the cabinet at the corner and put the knife inside the cabinet.
Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up a potato slice from the end of the potato.
Turn around and walk to the oven.
Put the potato slice in the front left pan.
Pick up the pan with the potato slice.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the pan with the slice of potato in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a potato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Head towards the sinks on the right.
Pick up the knife in front of the left-most sink.
Turn towards the front of the right-most sink.
With the knife, slice the fruit in the sink.
Turn left with the knife and head towards the black oven.
Open the second door of the bottom cabinet to the right of the oven and place the knife in it.
Head back towards the right-most sink.
Pick up a slice of the fruit in the right-most sink.
Turn right and head towards the white oven stove.
Place the slice of fruit on top of the near-right oven burner.
Pick up the silver tray on top of the near-left oven burner.
Turn left and head towards the refrigerator.
Place the silver tray in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Slice a fruit and place a tray in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and stop at the left of the sink
Grab the knife that is in front of the sink
Move slightly to the right
Cut the potato in the sink into slices
Turn left and look down at the cabinets on the bottom
Put the knife in the cabinet in the corner
Turn right and go to the right of the sink
Grab a slice of potato in the sink
Turn around and go to the oven
Put the potato in the bowl in the bottom left stove
Grab the bowl off the bottom left stove
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with a sliced potato in it in the fridge
